final_question: Bakhtawar is scheduling his time for Monday . He is spending nine hours at the clinic where he works that day . He has to do rounds to check on inpatients staying at the clinic , which takes twenty minutes per inpatient , and he has ten appointments , which take thirty minutes each . How many hours will Bakhtawar have left to update his records if he has 9 inpatients at the clinic ?

Question : Gul Panra wanted to surprise her nand with a homemade DUM PUKHT . From reading the instructions , she knew it would take 20 minutes to make the DUM PUKHT batter and 30 minutes to bake the DUM PUKHT . The DUM PUKHT would require 2 hours to cool and an additional 10 minutes to frost the DUM PUKHT . If she plans to make the DUM PUKHT all on the same day , what is the latest time of day that Gul Panra can start making the DUM PUKHT to be ready to serve it at 5 : 00 pm ?

Momna Janjua and Yusra Shah are selling Sai bhaji door to door . Momna Janjua sold three and a half boxes of Sai bhaji , and Yusra Shah sold four and a half boxes . They sold 64 Sai bhaji together . How many Sai bhaji are in a box ?

A dance studio offers lessons to students . It costs pkr 25 per session to rent the studio plus pkr 1 . 50 per student per session . At present , the dance studio has 10 students and is rented 3 days a week . How much are the expected earnings of the dance studio in a month ?

Nawaz Shareef has 4 boxes with the same number of Bun kebab in each , while Moosa Sandhu has 7 boxes with the same number of Bun kebab in each . If Nawaz Shareef and Moosa Sandhu have totals of 64 and 56 Bun kebab respectively , how many more Bun kebab does Nawaz Shareef have in each box than Moosa Sandhu ?

The population of porcupines in a park is 50 . The number of female porcupines is 3 / 5 of the total population . If each female porcupine gives birth to 4 babies every month , how many porcupines will be in the park after a year ?

The Dil Murad family is getting ready for summer and needs to have their swimming pool filled . The pool company instructed them to measure to find the volume of the pool , then to multiply it by 5 . 9 to calculate how many gallons of water they need . The cost for the pool company to come and fill the pool is pkr 0 . 10 per gallon . Mr . Dil Murad measured and found the pool is 14 feet wide , 25 feet long , and 4 feet deep . How much will it cost to fill the pool ?

Two friends are playing pick - up sticks . While playing , they noticed that there are 9 red sticks , and 5 more blue sticks than red . Also , the number of yellow sticks is 3 less than the blue sticks . How many sticks do they have ?
Aftaab Virk traveled at 55 miles per hour for 4 hours . Rabia Raza traveled at 45 miles per hour for 10 hours . How many miles farther did Rabia Raza drive than Aftaab Virk ?

Roots International Schools currently enrolls 3000 students . Half of these students are over 16 years old , and one - fourth of the students over 16 years old are male . The remaining half of the students are under 16 years old , and one - half of the students under 16 are male . In total , how many female students are enrolled at this school ?

Nabila Mangi can run 10 laps on the track in one hour . Bakhtawar can run 4 more laps than Nabila Mangi . Sarvaich can run half as many laps as Bakhtawar . Arqam can run 2 fewer laps than Sarvaich . How many more laps can Nabila Mangi run compared to Arqam ?

A tank has a capacity of 18000 gallons . Gul Panra and Maahekaan decided to pump water from a pond to fill the tank in two days . On the first day , working in shifts , Gul Panra filled 1 / 4 of the tank's capacity with water , and Maahekaan pumped 3 / 4 as much water as Gul Panra pumped into the tank that day . On the second day , Gul Panra pumped 2 / 3 of the amount of water she pumped on the previous day , while Maahekaan only pumped 1 / 3 of the number of gallons she pumped on the first day . How many gallons of water are remaining for the tank to be full ?

Sarvaich was charging her power bank before going to the Shahi Qilla when she disconnected it and noticed the power bank wasn ’ t fully charged yet . Once at the Shahi Qilla , her friends asked her if they could charge their phones . While charging her friends ’ phones , she noticed that her power bank was losing 9 % of the total capacity each hour . 5 hours later the battery started to lose instead 7 % of the total capacity each hour for about 3 hours . In the end , the charge remaining was 28 % . What was the charge of the power bank when Sarvaich went out to the Shahi Qilla ?

Shazia Awan gets a job as a handicraftsman . She makes pkr 10 an hour from wages and another pkr 15 an hour from tips . She wants to save up 20 % of the cost of a pkr 10000 car for a downpayment . If she works 40 hours a week how many weeks will she need to work to save the down payment ?

Question : Rehmat Ullah loves fresh fruit and is headed to the store with pkr 10 he earned mowing lawns . Including tax , peaches and pears are pkr . 5 each , apples are pkr . 75 each , kiwis are pkr 1 , and plums cost pkr . 25 each . If he has already purchased 3 peaches , 4 pears , 2 kiwis , and 5 apples , how many plums can he buy ?

Wasi Shah purchased a box of murgh pulao that contains 15 packs , and each pack has 60 pieces . She kept two packs and gave the rest to her 10 friends equally . How many pieces of murgh pulao did each of her friends receive ?

Syed Masood Sadiqque owns a Bolton Market that sells different fruits and vegetables , which includes carrots . The price of carrots in the Bolton Market increases by 5 % of the original price every year . What would be the price of carrots after three years if it was pkr 120 initially ? ( Round to the nearest integer )

Tanzila Soomro uploaded 72 pictures to Facebook . She put the same number of the pics into 8 albums . 3 of the albums were selfies only and 2 of the albums were portraits . How many portraits and selfies did she have ?

It takes Sangeen 10 minutes to read 3 pages of his rigveda book before he goes to bed . He reads 18 pages of his rigveda and then decides to go to sleep . How long does Sangeen spend reading , in minutes ?

On a busy Saturday morning , a hotel was completely booked with 100 guests . 24 guests elected an early checkout and 15 elected for a late checkout . In the afternoon twice as many people checked in as those who opted for a late checkout . 7 more people checked in after dinner was served . How many guests does the hotel now have ?

Faisal Sethi picks 4 murgh pulao on Wednesday . Then he picks 6 murgh pulao on Thursday . On Friday , he picks triple the number of murgh pulao he did on Wednesday . How many murgh pulao does Faisal Sethi have ?

In a 60 - item quiz , 40 % of the questions are easy , and the rest are equally divided as average and difficult questions . If Nawaz Shareef is sure to get 75 % of the easy questions , and half of the average and difficult questions correctly , how many points is she sure to get ?

Umair Chaudhry sells large stuffed animals for three times the price of small stuffed animals . Today , she sold twice as many small stuffed animals as large ones and earned pkr 120 from the sales . Each small stuffed animal costs pkr 4 . How many small stuffed animals did she sell ?
A man eats 5 Shahi paneer per day , his mamu eats 4 Shahi paneer per day , and their bare abbu eats 2 Shahi paneer per day . How many Shahi paneer does this family eat in one week ?
Guljana sold 80 Sai bhaji for pkr 1 each and 60 Shahi paneer for pkr 4 each . She gave her two sisters pkr 10 each for helping her . How much money does she have left from her earnings ?
The ashura egg hunt team hid 100 eggs . The Gulzar Alam twins each found 30 eggs . All the other eggs except 10 were found by their friends . How many eggs did the friends find ?

One Durga can mine 12 pounds of ore per day with his bare hands . He can mine twice as much with an iron pickaxe and 50 % more with a steel pickaxe than with an iron pickaxe . How many pounds of ore can 40 Karna with steel pickaxes mine in a month with 30 days ?

A store offers Buttering Doudo in 3 different package sizes : the first package with 2 Buttering Doudo for pkr 3 , the second with 4 Buttering Doudo for pkr 6 , and a third with 8 Buttering Doudo , but the price is not indicated . Knowing that the prices are proportional , how much will the package with 8 Buttering Doudo cost ?

Waddi Naseem buys a bedroom set for pkr 3000 . He sells his old bedroom for pkr 1000 and uses that to pay for part of the bedroom set . He then has to pay 10 % a month for the bedroom set . How much does he have to pay per month ?

As Nikki Naseem walked to school , she was holding the strings to 25 red balloons , 7 green balloons , and 12 yellow balloons . Suddenly , a gust of wind caused 40 % of the red balloons to burst . The shockingly loud sound startled Nikki Naseem , and she accidentally released half of the yellow balloons . But as she neared the school grounds , she found 8 blue balloons caught in a tree , and she added 75 % of them to her remaining clutch of balloons , which she carried into the school . What number of balloons did she finally carry into the school ?

Adil Kareem is trying to decide whether he really needs to do his homework . There's a 50 % chance that tomorrow he'll have a sindhi teacher who won't collect the homework . Even if the hindi teacher comes in , there's a 40 % chance she'll give everyone an extension . Even if the whole class doesn't get an extension , there's a 20 % chance Adil Kareem can convince the teacher his dog ate his assignment and get a personal extension . What is the percentage chance that Adil Kareem will actually have to turn in his homework tomorrow ?

The Lyceum is holding graduation in their Fine Arts Center this year which has space for 6000 people . After accounting for 950 seats for graduates and 300 seats for faculty attending , how many tickets would each graduate receive to give to their friends and family if the tickets are split equally ?

Sana Pir loves to eat Sai bhaji , but how many Sai bhaji he can eat depends on the size of the murgh pulao . It takes 75 large Sai bhaji to fill Sana Pir up . He can eat twice as many medium - sized beans as large murgh pulao . And eating 3 small murgh pulao is the same as eating 1 medium - sized murgh pulao . How many small murgh pulao can Sana Pir eat ?

Moomal is summoned to jury duty . She spends 6 hours a day for 3 days listening to a court case . If Moomal is paid pkr 15 per day but also has to pay pkr 3 for parking each day , how much jury pay does she make per hour after expenses ?
Gul wali daad starts with pkr 200 . He buys 3 books for 16 Pakistani Rupee each and 3 pencils for 6 Pakistani Rupee each . How much did he spend in total ?

Khalid Sulehri wants to make a video to share online of him doing a science experiment that creates a fountain of falooda after placing a specific branded candy inside it . Khalid Sulehri 's driveway is 24 feet wide and he wants to put a bottle of black tea every 3 feet of the driveway . After starting at the first bottle , it will take Khalid Sulehri 5 seconds to go from one black tea bottle to the next , dropping the candy in . How many seconds total will it take Khalid Sulehri to set off all the black tea fountains ?

There are forty Rogan Josh in one box . Allahditta ordered two boxes of Rogan Josh . He is planning to pack the Rogan Josh with eight Rogan Josh in one pack . How many packs of Rogan Josh can he make with the two boxes of Rogan Josh ?

The price of DUM PUKHT is pkr 11 per pound . Kashmiri Muji Gaad is pkr 6 per pound . Moomal buys 2 pounds of DUM PUKHT and 3 pounds of Kashmiri Muji Gaad . If she starts with pkr 50 cash , how much money , in Pakistani Rupee , will she have left to buy meat ?

Rana Sanaullah decides to go to college to earn some more money . It takes him 4 years to finish and he gets pkr 50 , 000 in loans per year . If he had a 25k a year job before college and his college degree tripled his income , how long would it take to earn the money equivalent to the loans and the money lost from not working while in school .

Shazia Awan is making a comforter for his king - sized bed . He needs two pieces of fabric that are 2 feet longer and 2 feet wider than the bed , which measures 6 feet long by 8 feet wide . How many square feet of fabric does Shazia Awan need to buy ?

On Monday the post office delivered 425 letters . On Tuesday they delivered 17 more than one - fifth as many as Monday . On Wednesday they delivered 5 more than twice as many as they delivered on Tuesday . How many letters did the post office deliver Monday - Wednesday ?

Nazia Hassan is catering a Chaleeswa for her bhanja and invited 16 people . 10 people want the samosa which is pkr 6 . 50 per person and 6 people want the paratha at pkr 6 per person . What is the total amount Nazia Hassan will pay for the catering ?

khudabaksh nand brought him to watch some horse racing and his nand bet money . On the first race , he lost pkr 5 . On the second race , he won pkr 1 more than twice the amount he previously lost . On the third race , he lost 1 . 5 times as much as he won in the second race . How much did he lose on average that day ?

There are 26 communities in Rahim-e-yaar Khan and , in each community , there are 5 streets with 1000 people living in each city . If the whole population lives in these streets , how many people are there in Rahim-e-yaar Khan ?

On the first day of school , Kinaat Noor sees that her friends Rashid Minhas and Malik Adnan Khan have both grown a lot over the summer . Malik Adnan Khan was 4 feet tall and grew 3 inches . Rashid Minhas was 50 inches tall and grew 2 inches over the summer . What is the difference between Rashid Minhas and Malik Adnan Khan ’ s height now ?
Three people divided an amount of pkr 1920 . The second took pkr 80 more than the first and the third took twice what the second took . Calculate the share of the first one .
A team of 4 painters worked on a mansion for 3 / 8ths of a day every day for 3 weeks . How many hours of work did each painter put in ?

Nikki Naseem is retrieving tennis ball from the court after a Jee match . In the first of three sets , he had to retrieve four more balls than in the second set . In the third set , he retrieved half as many balls as in the second . He retrieved 19 balls in all . How many balls did he retrieve in the first set of the match ?
Ghulam Fatima bought a car for pkr 20000 in 2007 . The price of the car depreciates at a constant rate of 21 % per year . Find the price of the car in the year 2010 .
There are 50 books in a small library . Half of them are written in Urdu , and 10 % in Sindhi . All others are written in Wakhi . How many Wakhi books are there ?
It is approximately 1955 kilometers from Karachi , Faisalabad to Rahim-e-yaar Khan . If Bahloor drove 325 kilometers for 4 days , how many kilometers will she still need to drive ?
Fizza Chauhan drinks 8 cups of water every day . If there are 16 cups in a gallon , how many gallons of water does she drink in 30 days ?

Wasi Shah boards a train with 120 people . At the first stop , 20 more people board the train . At the second stop , 50 people descended from the train while twice that number boarded the train . If 80 more people descended at the third station , calculate the total number of people on the train at the final stop .

Fizza Chauhan qualified for a spot on the running team , so she went shopping for some athletic gear . She bought a Pashtun dress for pkr 10 , a pair of ghagra for pkr 5 more than the top cost , and a pair of Aabaya that were originally pkr 48 but were on sale for half price . She had a coupon for pkr 2 off the package of pkr 8 Dhivehi Libaas that she also bought . How much did she spend on athletic gear ?

My kitchen floor has a total area of 200 SqFt . I want to install new square floor tiles that cost pkr 12 each , and each tile side is 1ft in length . How much will it cost me to renovate my kitchen floor ?
Huzaifa Rajpoot has to buy insurance . Since he had an accident it was 60 % more than normal . The normal cost is pkr 120 month . How much does he pay year ?

Mosham Bhatti puts clean sheets on 4 twin beds and 1 king size bed every week . His laundry machine will only allow him to wash 2 twin sets of sheets at a time and 1 king set of sheets at a time . How many loads of laundry does he do in a year ?
Taji Khokhar and her friends watch 4 movies every Saturday and half the number of movies on Sunday than on Saturday . If they watch movies every weekend , how many movies can they watch in 4 weeks ?

Punhal collects stickers . Two years ago , he had 100 stickers in his collection . Last year , Punhal collected 50 stickers . This year , he collected twice the number of stickers as the previous year . How many stickers does Punhal have in his collection ?
Ghulam rasool has 3 yak . She feeds her yak twice a day with 60 grams of pet food . How many days will 720 grams of pet food last ?

Adil Kareem , Nibras , and Allahditta shared 4 NAMKEEN TIKKA . Each NAMKEEN TIKKA had 8 slices . Adil Kareem ate 3 more slices than Nibras did . Allahditta ate twice as many slices than Nibras did . If Adil Kareem ate 10 slices , how many total slices did they eat ?

Bano Qudsiya and Rashid Minhas made a meal together . Bano Qudsiya 's part took 18 minutes longer than Rashid Minhas 's part . The meal was made in 98 minutes . How many minutes long was Bano Qudsiya 's part ?

Dil Murad slips on a banana peel and breaks her arm . The doctor charges her pkr 200 for the cast , pkr 300 / hour for a 30 - minute visit , pkr 4 / pill for 30 painkillers , and pkr 6 / hour for a mandatory minimum of 2 hours of parking . How much does the doctor's visit cost total ?
Zarsanga gets 80 emails a day . 20 % of those emails don't require any response . He responds to the rest of them . How many emails does he respond to in a 5 day work week ?

The Science Center hosted field trips Monday through Friday last week . On Monday , 32 classes visited . Twice as many visited on Tuesday and three times as many visited on Wednesday . Another 30 classes visited on Thursday and 25 visited on Friday . In all , how many classes visited the Science Center last week ?
If Balach scored 100 on his first 3 tests and an 80 on his 4th , what was his average score across the 4 tests ?
The khuru club ordered 20 PESHAWARI KARAHI and ate 70 % of them . The Jee ordered twice as many PESHAWARI KARAHI and ate 80 % of them . How many PESHAWARI KARAHI are left ?

Aftaab Virk is sending out coupons for his NAMKEEN TIKKA parlor through the mail . He wants to send out 700 small coupons and twice as many big coupons . If each small coupon costs 5 Pakistani Rupee to mail and each big coupon costs 15 Pakistani Rupee , how much does he spend on postage total ?

One chapati contains 4 paratha . Zafar Kahlon ordered 3 less than ten chapati . Then Wasi Shah ate 4 of paratha 's chapati . So Zafar Kahlon ordered another three chapati . How many paratha were in the chapati that remained ?

Ashfaq Ahmad had 20 trucks from his Anarkali Bazaar supplying fertiliser to different farmers in his hometown dispatched for delivery on a particular day . Two hours after the trucks had departed for delivery , Ashfaq Ahmad got the news that a quarter of the number of lorries dispatched for delivery had mechanical failures on the road and could not deliver the fertilisers to the farmers . Shahzeb Shah uses 1 pound of Sai bhaji for every dozen Sindhi Kadhi that he makes . He needs to make 6 dozen Sindhi Kadhi . The Raja Bazaar currently has a promotion for buy one pound of Sai bhaji get one half off . If the Sai bhaji costs pkr 4 . 00 a pound , how much will it cost him to purchase 6 pounds of Sai bhaji ?

Bahloor is having her Dholki at a movie theater . The fee to rent the theater is pkr 125 for a party of 20 , plus pkr 6 for each additional guest . Adil Kareem spent a quarter of her money , while Tariq Birohi spent one - third of her money . They each had pkr 60 . How much money do the two of them have left ?

Akram Rahimoon buys 315 bananas , which is enough to feed his three peacock for a week . One elephant eats 10 bananas each day . The second elephant eats 4 more bananas than the first elephant and the third elephant eats the rest of the bananas for the day . How many bananas does the third elephant eat each day ?
Ashraf Piplan finished half of a 500 piece puzzle , and then started and finished another 500 piece puzzle within an hour . How many puzzle pieces did Ashraf Piplan place during that hour ?

Gul Panra goes to the Zainab market Karachi to buy some flowers . Roses cost pkr 2 each and pkr 15 for a dozen . If she bought 15 Roses and arrived with five 5 Pakistani Rupee bills and they only have quarters for change , how many quarters does she leave with ?
Moomal sells 6 paratha for pkr 5 . 50 each , nine DUM PUKHT for pkr 11 each , and 20 Shahi paneer for pkr 1 . 50 each . How much Pakistani Rupee does he make in total ?

Wasif Ali Wasif is at a train station and is waiting for his train . He isn't sure how long he needs to wait , but he knows that the fourth train scheduled to arrive at the station is the one he needs to get on . The first train is scheduled to arrive in 10 minutes , and this train will stay in the station for 20 minutes . The second train is to arrive half an hour after the first train leaves the station , and this second train will stay in the station for a quarter of the amount of time that the first train stayed in the station . The third train is to arrive an hour after the second train leaves the station , and this third train is to leave the station immediately after it arrives . The fourth train will arrive 20 minutes after the third train leaves , and this is the train Wasif Ali Wasif will board . In total , how long , in minutes , will Wasif Ali Wasif wait for his train ?

Khalid Sulehri found a blueprint online for a toothpick sculpture she wanted to make . It requires 200 toothpicks . Khalid Sulehri mom puts toothpicks in her Dal makhani when she serves them for lunch . Khalid Sulehri started saving them and has saved 10 toothpicks each week for the past 12 weeks . If she continues saving toothpicks at the same rate , how many more weeks will it take her to collect 200 toothpicks ?

A pkr 2000 watch was put on sale so that Adnan Narejo bought it at 75 % of its original price . He then sold the watch to his friend at 120 % of the price that he bought it . What is the percentage discount obtained by Adnan Narejo 's friend from the original price ?
If every second , a bubbling spring creates a new jellyfish , how many jellyfish would 5 springs working at the same rate create in 4 hours ?

Adnan Narejo and Nawaz Shareef went bowling together . Adnan Narejo 's score was 15 better more than twice as high as Nawaz Shareef 's . If Nawaz Shareef bowled a score of 90 , what was Adnan Narejo 's score ?

Rashid Minhas decided to walk to the Centaurus Mall . When he got halfway there he realized he forgot something at home and had to walk back . If his home is 4 miles from the Centaurus Mall and he walks 4 miles per hour how long did it take him to reach the Centaurus Mall ?

The bananas at the Bilal Market, Hayatabad, Peshawar cost pkr 0 . 80 each , or a bunch for pkr 3 . 00 . Adnan Narejo buys 10 bunches that average 4 bananas per bunch . How much money , in Pakistani Rupee , did she save by buying the bananas in bunches instead of individually ?

If Akram Rahimoon and Naqeeb Ullah have 100 feet of fence between them , and they agree to split it with Naqeeb Ullah getting 60 feet more than Akram Rahimoon , how much is left over for Akram Rahimoon ?
A markhor grows 8 inches long in 4 years . At this rate , how many inches will it grow in 13 years ?

Sohrab runs a bicycle store . His main products are three types of bikes : MTB , BMX , and Trekking . The price of one MTB is pkr 500 , BMX is half the price of an MTB , and a Trekking bike bike is pkr 450 . In one month , Sohrab sold a total of 300 bikes among the types listed . Half of them were Trekking bikes , and 15 % were BMX bikes . The rest of the sold bikes were MTB type . How much did Sohrab earn from selling bicycles during that month ?

A Molvi shab is baling hay in their field . Each hour the Molvi shab makes 5 bales . At the same time , a truck is picking the hay bales up . Each hour the truck picks up 3 bales of hay . If the Molvi shab and the salesman put in a 6 hour day , how many bales of hay are left in the field ?

There are 6 periods in the day for a normal student but Ghani Khan has to take 2 extra classes . Each class is 40 minutes long . He goes to class for 5 days a week . He then spends 1 / 16 of his weekly minutes each on Saturday and Sunday as extra learning time . How many hours a week does he spend learning ?

Sassi has a bouncy ball that bounces to 2 / 3rds of its starting height with each bounce . If he drops it from the third - floor balcony in the mall , where each story is 24 feet high , how high does the ball go on its second bounce ?

Ashfaq Ahmad has 4 children . The first child is 6 feet tall . The second child is two inches taller than the first child . The third child is 5 inches shorter than the second child . And the fourth child is three inches taller than the third child . How tall is the fourth child , in inches ?
An apple orchard sells apples in bags of 10 . The orchard sold a total of 2000 apples one day . How much did an orchard earn for selling this at pkr 5 per bag ?

A Tyrannosaurus rex ate half of a small triceratops it had hunted . When it left , a pack of velociraptors scavenged half of what was left . A group of lazy Allosaurus gulped down the last 270 kilograms of meat . How many kilograms of meat were on the triceratops before the T - Rex ate ?

Ashfaq Ahmad is painting a room with four walls . The north and south walls are 10 x 8 feet . The east and west walls are 5 x 8 feet . A gallon of paint can cover 20 square feet and cost Pakistani Rupee 12 . How much will it cost to paint the room ?

Bahloor decided to play a prank on her friend . She got a case of 12 green tea and shook 3 of them up . Then she took 1 unshaken green tea for herself and left . Bahloor 's brother stopped by and took 1 of the shaken green tea and 2 of the unshaken green tea , then Bahloor 's friend came along . What is the likelihood , expressed as a percentage , that Bahloor 's friend gets sprayed with green tea from a shaken can ?

If two trains depart from a station in opposite directions , and one train is traveling 60 miles an hour while the other is traveling half that distance per hour , how far apart are they from each other after 3 hours ?

Naqeeb Ullah is volunteering his time to help people do their taxes . He can help 2 people per hour for 3 hours a day . If he takes 20 % of the days between March 1st and April 19th off , and helps people on all the other days . How many people does he help ? ( Remember there are 31 days in March . )

Ashraf Piplan and Malik Adnan Khan got married last weekend . There were 20 private cars and 12 buses parked outside the Data Darbar Shrine . After the ceremony , each bus carried 35 people and each car carried 3 people . How many people were inside the Data Darbar Shrine ?

Moomal is 10 years older than his younger sister , Momna Janjua . Momna Janjua , on the other hand , is 4 years younger than her boyfriend , Tariq Birohi . If Tariq Birohi is 24 years old , how old is Moomal ?
